            <title>ColorOS 支持微信朋友圈 Live 图，OPPO / 一加 70+ 款机型陆续升级覆盖</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/846/382.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/846/382.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 14:27:09 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1420554" rel="nofollow">OkayTech</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D795776" rel="nofollow">風見暉一</a> 的线索投递！</div>
